Changes in v2:
- Add Nazar Kompanets as a co-developer on some patches
  - We both worked on independent IPA implementations
- Delete wrong note about SMEM size
  - When comparing downstream device trees from both SM8450 and SM8475
  based devices, they all use a fixed size of 0x9000
- Modify SRAM size in DT
- Properly organize patches and DT properties
